<img data-lazyloaded="1" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI4MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iOTYyIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgODAwIDk2MiI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgc3R5bGU9ImZpbGw6I2NmZDRkYjtmaWxsLW9wYWNpdHk6IDAuMTsiLz48L3N2Zz4=" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="800" height="962" data-src="https://nydcdubai.com/wp-content/uploads/NYDC-Website-2-852x1024.webp" class="attachment-large size-large wp-image-3733" alt="New York Dental Clinic" data-srcset="https://nydcdubai.com/wp-content/uploads/NYDC-Website-2-852x1024.webp 852w, https://nydcdubai.com/wp-content/uploads/NYDC-Website-2-250x300.webp 250w, https://nydcdubai.com/wp-content/uploads/NYDC-Website-2-768x923.webp 768w, https://nydcdubai.com/wp-content/uploads/NYDC-Website-2.webp 1260w" data-sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" title="Home 1"></div></div></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-4a771a46 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="4a771a46" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container"><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-5d6d4025 elementor-widget__width-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="5d6d4025" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><h1 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">New York Dental Clinic: Dental Practice in Dubai</h1></div></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-481bb29 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="481bb29" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><p><a href="https://nydcdubai.com/dentist-in-dubai/"><strong data-start="59" data-end="85">New York Dental Clinic</strong></a> is a premier dental practice in Dubai, led by Dr. Ajay Juneja, a renowned Prosthodontist with over two decades of experience. Since its establishment, the clinic has been dedicated to providing <strong data-start="280" data-end="295">responsible</strong> and advanced dentistry in a compassionate and professional environment. Specialising in a wide range of services from restorative treatments to aesthetic dentistry, the practice prides itself on using the <strong data-start="501" data-end="522">latest technology</strong> and techniques to ensure exceptional care for every patient. With a <strong data-start="591" data-end="617" data-is-only-node="">multidisciplinary team</strong> of specialists, New York Dental Clinic offers comprehensive, personalised solutions for all your dental needs.</p></div></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-19dabaa9 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="19dabaa9" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><p>New York Dental Clinic’s commitment to excellence is reflected in its approach to both patient care and clinical results. The clinic offers a <strong>welcoming and calming atmosphere</strong>, ensuring that every visit is a positive experience. From the latest in digital smile design to <strong>state-of-the-art equipment</strong>, each treatment is tailored to meet individual needs. With a team of skilled professionals dedicated to providing the highest standard of care, New York Dental Clinic has become a trusted choice for patients seeking reliable and effective dental solutions in Dubai. Your smile is in expert hands.</p></div></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-faf33f6 elementor-align-left elementor-widget elementor-widget-button" data-id="faf33f6" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="button.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><div class="elementor-button-wrapper">
<a class="elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm" href="#form">
<span class="elementor-button-content-wrapper">
<span class="elementor-button-text">Contact us</span>
</span>
</a></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-3b5fe1a e-con-full e-flex e-con e-parent" data-id="3b5fe1a" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container"><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-5b001c4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-template" data-id="5b001c4" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="template.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><div class="elementor-template"><div data-elementor-type="section" data-elementor-id="3805" class="elementor elementor-3805" data-elementor-post-type="elementor_library"><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-c4cc793 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent" data-id="c4cc793" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container" data-settings="{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}"><div class="e-con-inner"><div data-dce-background-overlay-image-url="https://nydcdubai.com/wp-content/uploads/NYDC-Website-5.webp" class="elementor-element elementor-element-af8a264 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="af8a264" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container" data-settings="{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}"><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-c225375 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="c225375" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><h3 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Responsible Dentistry</h3></div></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-0184f4d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="0184f4d" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><p><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none">We prioritize your oral health with a commitment to ethical practices and personalized care, ensuring a responsible and trustworthy dental experience.</span></p></div></div></div><div data-dce-background-overlay-image-url="https://nydcdubai.com/wp-content/uploads/NYDC-Website-1-2.webp" class="elementor-element elementor-element-a55a24c e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="a55a24c" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container" data-settings="{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}"><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-6d15479 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="6d15479" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><h3 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Compassion and Care</h3></div></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-ff12f46 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="ff12f46" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><p><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none">Beyond treating teeth, we embrace every patient with genuine warmth and empathy, fostering a compassionate environment where your well-being is as important as your dental health.</span></p></div></div></div><div data-dce-background-overlay-image-url="https://nydcdubai.com/wp-content/uploads/NYDC-Website-2-1.webp" class="elementor-element elementor-element-f0ce22c e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="f0ce22c" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container" data-settings="{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}"><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-351de07 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="351de07" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><h3 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Knowledged Dentistry</h3></div></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-fc23607 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="fc23607" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><p><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none">Empowering your smile with the latest advancements, our knowledgeable team blends expertise and innovation to deliver dentistry that is at the forefront of excellence.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-15b38fd e-con-full e-flex e-con e-parent" data-id="15b38fd" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container"><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-a6813a0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-template" data-id="a6813a0" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="template.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><div class="elementor-template"><div data-elementor-type="section" data-elementor-id="365" class="elementor elementor-365" data-elementor-post-type="elementor_library"><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-003028e e-con-full e-flex e-con e-parent" data-id="003028e" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container" id="dottore"><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-21d5fd8 e-con-full animated-fast e-flex elementor-invisible e-con e-child" data-id="21d5fd8" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container" data-settings="{&quot;animation&quot;:&quot;bounceInLeft&quot;}"><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-13f0734 dce_masking-none elementor-widget elementor-widget-image" data-id="13f0734" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="image.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container">
<img data-lazyloaded="1" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI4MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iODAwIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgODAwIDgwMCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgc3R5bGU9ImZpbGw6I2NmZDRkYjtmaWxsLW9wYWNpdHk6IDAuMTsiLz48L3N2Zz4=" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="800" height="800" data-src="https://nydcdubai.com/wp-content/uploads/NYDC-Dr-Ajay-Juneja-1024x1024.webp" class="attachment-large size-large wp-image-4396" alt="Dr. Ajay Juneja" data-srcset="https://nydcdubai.com/wp-content/uploads/NYDC-Dr-Ajay-Juneja-1024x1024.webp 1024w, https://nydcdubai.com/wp-content/uploads/NYDC-Dr-Ajay-Juneja-300x300.webp 300w, https://nydcdubai.com/wp-content/uploads/NYDC-Dr-Ajay-Juneja-150x150.webp 150w, https://nydcdubai.com/wp-content/uploads/NYDC-Dr-Ajay-Juneja-768x768.webp 768w, https://nydcdubai.com/wp-content/uploads/NYDC-Dr-Ajay-Juneja.webp 1080w" data-sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" title="Home 2"></div></div></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-5972b0f e-con-full animated-fast e-flex elementor-invisible e-con e-child" data-id="5972b0f" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container" data-settings="{&quot;animation&quot;:&quot;bounceInRight&quot;,&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}"><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-ca9dfbc elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="ca9dfbc" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container">
<span class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Owner, Prosthodontist</span></div></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-58706d5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="58706d5" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container">
<span class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Dr. Ajay Juneja </span></div></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-6984793 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="6984793" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><p><strong data-start="0" data-end="19" data-is-only-node="">Dr. Ajay Juneja</strong>, the founder and owner of <strong data-start="46" data-end="72">New York Dental Clinic</strong>, is a renowned Prosthodontist with a passion for esthetic dentistry. He completed his B.D.S and M.D.S in India and earned a Master&#8217;s in Esthetic Dentistry from UCLA, USA. With over 20 years of experience, Dr. Juneja has been an international speaker, sharing his expertise at numerous global conferences. He is a member of the prestigious <strong data-start="412" data-end="430">Style Italiano</strong> and serves as the <strong data-start="449" data-end="472">Country Chairperson</strong> for the <strong data-start="481" data-end="489">ESCD</strong> in the UAE. His commitment to responsible and advanced restorative dentistry ensures exceptional care for every patient at his clinic.</p></div></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-67d2092 elementor-widget elementor-widget-button" data-id="67d2092" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="button.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><div class="elementor-button-wrapper">
<a class="elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm" href="https://nydcdubai.com/dentist-dubai/">
<span class="elementor-button-content-wrapper">
<span class="elementor-button-text">Find out more</span>
</span>
