From the South (Jumeirah Beach)						</span></h3></div></div></div></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-fe033b5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="fe033b5" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><p><strong data-start="203" data-end="238">From the South (Jumeirah Beach)</strong>: Take Beach Road heading north. After passing Jumeirah Beach, continue straight, and the clinic will be on your right.</p></div></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-0121402 elementor-widget elementor-widget-ucaddon_dropdown_button" data-id="0121402" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="ucaddon_dropdown_button.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container">
<style>/* widget: Dropdown Button */

#uc_dropdown_button_elementor_0121402 {
  display:flex;
  align-items: center;
}

#uc_dropdown_button_elementor_0121402 .ca_btn_container{
  position: relative;
  display: inline-block;
}

#uc_dropdown_button_elementor_0121402 .ca_btn {
  display:inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  overflow: hidden;
  cursor: pointer;
}

#uc_dropdown_button_elementor_0121402 .ca_btn .ca_dropdown {
  width:100%;
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  transform: translate(-50%, 25px);
  position: absolute;
  top: 100%;
  left:50%;
  text-align: left;
  opacity: 0;
  visibility: hidden;
  z-index:9999;
  overflow: hidden;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
}

#uc_dropdown_button_elementor_0121402 .ca_btn.ue_active_drop .ca_dropdown {
  left:50%;
  transform: translate(-50%, 10px);
  opacity: 1;
  visibility: visible;
  transition-delay: 0ms;
}


#uc_dropdown_button_elementor_0121402 .ca_btn .ca_dropdown li {
  z-index: 1;
  position: relative;
  margin: 0;
  list-style: none;
  margin: 0;
  display: inline;
}

#uc_dropdown_button_elementor_0121402 .ca_btn .ca_dropdown li:last-child a {
  border-bottom: 0;
}

#uc_dropdown_button_elementor_0121402 .ca_btn .ca_dropdown a {
  transition:300ms;
  display: flex;
  align-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  border-bottom-style: solid;
  white-space: pre-line;
  text-decoration: none;
}

#uc_dropdown_button_elementor_0121402 .ca_dropdown i{
  transition:300ms;
}

