></iframe></div></div></div></div><div data-dce-background-color="#F0F0F0" id="e-n-tab-content-1939763742" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="e-n-tab-title-1939763742" data-tab-index="2" style="--n-tabs-title-order: 2;" class=" elementor-element elementor-element-9596516 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="9596516" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container" data-settings="{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}"><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-8919e76 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="8919e76" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><ul><li data-start="1308" data-end="1428"><p data-start="1311" data-end="1428"><strong data-start="1311" data-end="1327">From Al Safa</strong>: Take Al Wasl Road heading south. Turn right onto Beach Road and continue straight for the clinic.</p></li><li data-start="1430" data-end="1564"><p data-start="1433" data-end="1564"><strong data-start="1433" data-end="1456">From <a href="https://nydcdubai.com/dental-clinic-in-jumeirah/">Jumeirah Beach</a></strong>: Head north on Beach Road; the clinic will be on your right-hand side, just past the Jumeirah Beach area.</p></li><li data-start="1566" data-end="1719"><p data-start="1569" data-end="1719"><strong data-start="1569" data-end="1590">From <a href="https://nydcdubai.com/dental-clinic-in-dubai-marina/">Dubai Marina</a></strong>: Drive along Sheikh Zayed Road, exit at Al Wasl Road, and head towards Beach Road. Turn left, and the clinic is on your right.</p></li><li data-start="1721" data-end="1874"><p data-start="1724" data-end="1874"><strong data-start="1724" data-end="1747">From Downtown Dubai</strong>: Take Sheikh Zayed Road heading west, exit at Al Wasl Road, and turn left onto Beach Road. Continue straight for the clinic.</p></li><li data-start="1876" data-end="2054" data-is-last-node=""><strong data-start="92" data-end="114">From <a href="https://nydcdubai.com/dental-clinic-in-business-bay/">Business Bay</a>:</strong> Drive along Sheikh Zayed Road heading west toward Jumeirah. Take the exit for Al Wasl Road and continue straight toward Beach Road. Turn left onto Beach Road, and the clinic will be on your right-hand side.</li></ul></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-a2aaee6 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-parent" data-id="a2aaee6" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container"><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-65dd01d elementor-widget elementor-widget-template" data-id="65dd01d" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="template.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><div class="elementor-template"><div data-elementor-type="section" data-elementor-id="637" class="elementor elementor-637" data-elementor-post-type="elementor_library"><div data-dce-background-color="#FFFFFF" class="elementor-element elementor-element-8fa0a6d animated-fast e-flex e-con-boxed elementor-invisible e-con e-parent" data-id="8fa0a6d" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container" data-settings="{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;,&quot;animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInLeft&quot;}"><div class="e-con-inner"><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-a42ebd6 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="a42ebd6" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container"><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-aafe25a elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="aafe25a" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container">
